---
import Layout from "@/layouts/Layout.astro";
import Container from "@/components/container.astro";
---

<Layout title="About">
  <Container>

    <!-- Hero -->
    <div class="text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto mt-16 mb-20">
      <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-violet-700 uppercase tracking-wide">Our Story</p>
      <h1 class="text-5xl font-bold mt-4 text-slate-800 leading-tight">
        Built by a parent, <span class="text-violet-700">for every family</span>
      </h1>
      <p class="text-lg text-slate-500 mt-6 leading-relaxed">
        UniqueApex was born from a deeply personal experience — navigating the overwhelming, fragmented world of neurodevelopmental support as a parent. We built the infrastructure families deserve.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Mission -->
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center mb-24">
      <div>
        <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-violet-700 uppercase tracking-wide">Our Mission</p>
        <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold mt-3 text-slate-800 leading-tight">
          Coordination infrastructure, <span class="text-violet-700">not just a directory</span>
        </h2>
        <p class="text-slate-500 mt-6 leading-relaxed text-lg">
          Families of neurodivergent children don't lack services — they lack the infrastructure to access them. UniqueApex fills that gap with a structured, automated coordination layer that works for families from first concern through ongoing care.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="rounded-2xl overflow-hidden">
        <img src="/2.png" alt="Family illustration" class="w-full object-cover" />
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Values -->
    <div class="mb-24">
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-violet-700 uppercase tracking-wide">Our Values</p>
        <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold mt-3 text-slate-800">What we stand for</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
        <div class="bg-slate-50 rounded-2xl p-8">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-violet-700">Empathy</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-500 mt-3 leading-relaxed">We start with the family. Every decision we make is grounded in the real experience of parents navigating an overwhelming system.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-slate-50 rounded-2xl p-8">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-violet-700">Clarity</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-500 mt-3 leading-relaxed">No jargon, no confusion. We make complex systems simple so families can focus on their child — not on paperwork.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-slate-50 rounded-2xl p-8">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-violet-700">Access</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-500 mt-3 leading-relaxed">Every child deserves support regardless of language, location, or how overwhelmed their parents feel. We remove barriers, not add them.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-slate-50 rounded-2xl p-8">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-violet-700">Community</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-500 mt-3 leading-relaxed">No family navigates alone. UniqueApex connects families with each other, with experts, and with the providers who can actually help.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Founder -->
    <div class="bg-slate-50 rounded-2xl p-10 md:p-16 mb-24">
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-12 items-center">
        <div class="flex flex-col items-center text-center">
          <img
            src="/headshot.jpeg"
            alt="Pelin İpek Temurcan"
            class="w-48 h-48 rounded-full object-cover shadow-lg"
          />
          <h3 class="font-bold text-xl mt-4 text-slate-800">Pelin İpek Temurcan</h3>
          <p class="text-violet-700 font-medium">Founder & CEO</p>
        </div>
        <div class="md:col-span-2">
          <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-violet-700 uppercase tracking-wide">A message from our Founder</p>
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mt-3 text-slate-800 leading-tight">
            "I built what I wish had existed."
          </h2>
          <p class="text-slate-500 mt-6 leading-relaxed text-lg">
            When I started navigating the support system for my child, I was shocked by how fragmented everything was. I had to contact each provider individually, re-explain the same story over and over, and wait months with no visibility into where things stood. I have a background in project management and architecture — and even I found it overwhelming. I can only imagine how it feels for families who don't have that toolkit.
          </p>
          <p class="text-slate-500 mt-4 leading-relaxed text-lg">
            UniqueApex is the coordination layer that should have always existed. We are starting in Montréal, serving English and French-speaking families, and we are just getting started.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

  </Container>
</Layout>